Man finds buffalo in his swimming pool
A man in the United States had to haul a buffalo from his swimming pool after finding the creature hiding under the cover.
By Myles Burke
11:30AM BST 26 Oct 2010
Chris Nonnemaker of White County, Georgia, discovered the escaped animal when his wife, Alison, noticed holes in the pool cover. He pulled back the cover to find that a buffalo had become stuck in the pool after escaping from a neighbour's herd. The sheriff’s deputies and animal's owner were called to the house and managed to pull the beast from the water by lassoing it around the horns. Related Articles
